folder: Piers 6 and 7 of the United Fruit Company., Hudson River, Manhattan, NY
text:
North (Hudson) River, showing piers 7 and 8, off West Street, at the foot of Rector Street. Also shown is part of Lower Manhattan's skyline.

August 31, 1926.

P. L. Sperr.
title: North (Hudson) River - Piers 6 and 7 of the United Fruit Company.
